# Tag a Release
Step 1 --> increment the semantic version in the zarr_manager.py "metadata" & the "pyproject.toml"
```commandline
git tag -a v25.1.8 -m "Releasing version v25.1.8"
git push origin --tags
```

# To Publish To PROD
```commandline
uv build
python -m twine upload --repository pypi dist/*
```

